---
layout: base.njk
title: Unmade
description: A scrollable archive of things that almost existed.
permalink: /unmade/
---
<main class="archive-page">
  <nav class="topbar" aria-label="Unmade navigation">
    <a class="wordmark" href="/unmade/">Unmade</a>
    <a class="home-link" href="#archive">Archive</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="kicker">Scroll archive / things that almost existed</p>
      <h1>Unmade</h1>
      <p>Unsent words and signals, unbuilt places, products, and software, and unheld lives, relationships, roles, and futures that never found a surface.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="hero-image">
      <img src="/unmade/assets/images/topic-contact-sheet.png" alt="Image grid representing the three Unmade archive topics">
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section class="topic-grid" aria-label="Archive topics">
    {% set topics = [
      { label: "Unsent", summary: "Words and signals." },
      { label: "Unbuilt", summary: "Places, products, and software." },
      { label: "Unheld", summary: "Lives, relationships, roles, and futures." }
    ] %}
    {% for topic in topics %}
      <a class="topic-card" href="#{{ topic.label | lower }}">
        <img src="/unmade/assets/images/topic-{{ topic.label | lower }}.png" alt="{{ topic.label }} visual study">
        <span>{{ topic.label }}</span>
        <p>{{ topic.summary }}</p>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <p>This is not a productivity site or a portfolio in the usual sense. It is a public index of possible things: fragments, case files, prototypes, scenes, notes, and artifacts from work that was imagined but not completed.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="entry-stream" id="archive" aria-label="Unmade entries">
    {% for entry in collections.unmade | reverse %}
      <article id="{{ entry.data.category | lower }}" class="entry-card">
        <a href="{{ entry.url }}">
          <div>
            <p class="kicker">{{ entry.data.category }} / {{ entry.data.status }}</p>
            <h2>{{ entry.data.title }}</h2>
            <p>{{ entry.data.excerpt }}</p>
          </div>
          <span class="entry-object artifact-{{ entry.data.visual }}" aria-hidden="true">{{ entry.data.mark }}</span>
          <span class="open-label" aria-hidden="true">Open case</span>
        </a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
</main>
